# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians7.rpy:25
translate russian adrians7_df5c3fd6:

    # pc "Yeah, that would definitely take a special sort of superpower."
    pc "Да, для этого точно понадобилась бы особая суперсила."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians7.rpy:27
translate russian adrians7_eaec1847:

    # gg "Ha! You're telling me!"
    gg "Ха! Мне ли не знать!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians7.rpy:28
translate russian adrians7_e0eff7f6:

    # gg "Never gonna happen."
    gg "Этого никогда не будет."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/AdrianConversations/adrians7.rpy:30
translate russian adrians7_40ebac00:

    # gg "So I just have to keep ignoring jerks or telling them to go fuck themselves."
